{"tid":2058684,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"話說我係隻俾領養左既狐狸，成日俾人當做狗","createTime":"2020-06-10T10:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T16:21:23.000Z","uid":253883,"like":23,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9d0c2693b1075f4d4dbb4e1d7563b5da3f0fbd14","tid":2058684,"uid":253883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:46:00.000Z","msg":"聽講我係到都略有名氣 <br />\n<br />\n所以想開個post<br />\n<br />\n話說<br />\n<br />\n有一日我俾人帶左去一個籠<br />\n<br />\n上下都係好嘈既狗<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪我係狐狸<br />\n<br />\n無人想抱我<br />\n<br />\n直到第二日<br />\n<br />\n有個怪人抱左我出黎<br />\n<br />\n隔左好多日黑暗<br />\n<br />\n好似理大圍城咁多個無助既黑暗夜晚<br />\n<br />\n我俾果個怪人帶走左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5rjPmQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5rjPmQ.jpg&h=7e3327e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話咁快 <br />\n<br />\n就同個怪人住左半年 <br />\n<br />\n雖然我講唔到野  唔會開口要求野<br />\n<br />\n但怪人都晚晚都帶我出街街 <br />\n<br />\n而唔知點解呢排出街街好似少左聞到攻鼻怪味<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之 <br />\n<br />\n有怪人同行既呢半年<br />\n<br />\n有零食有人陪 開心豬<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好再誤會我係狗啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0wBG2JC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0wBG2JC.jpg&h=9a6cb121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎緊既日子唔知會略<br />\n<br />\n我叫左怪人多d幫我出post<br />\n<br />\n希望<br />\n<br />\n大家仲會上到連登<br />\n<br />\n同我一齊行落去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定會架可<br />\n<br />\n哈姆太朗"},{"pid":"59718c6142a6b4252d404ad1d16c5cc88a99ff42","tid":2058684,"uid":226902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:47:00.000Z","msg":"真係狐狸？"},{"pid":"c4a019870314b573547890710e812cdcfe076c95","tid":2058684,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1cc3cb59a2d3dfce07eb522131f675589d8cc9","tid":2058684,"uid":124983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:47:34.000Z","msg":"What does the fox say<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa861aa293acb2ae590924738ce0614cd7507580","tid":2058684,"uid":253883,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"59718c6142a6b4252d404ad1d16c5cc88a99ff42","tid":2058684,"uid":226902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:47:00.000Z","msg":"真係狐狸？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:48:35.000Z","msg":"唔好報海關 應承我"},{"pid":"a7358924ac4f167a0732b4d3cde177de18106922","tid":2058684,"uid":253883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf1cc3cb59a2d3dfce07eb522131f675589d8cc9","tid":2058684,"uid":124983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:47:34.000Z","msg":"What does the fox say<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"講到爛啦個gag"},{"pid":"7ef91e800d786bfb6ccc8b7ccf9480d231b55589","tid":2058684,"uid":273157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:49:27.000Z","msg":"狗黎嫁，唔好呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34017b2411195fab012b203988be1cbbf77dc44e","tid":2058684,"uid":32947,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:57:09.000Z","msg":"好心你俾隻狗瞓覺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7140be2347370d8ab3d1b480fc3c69a431c3b0","tid":2058684,"uid":253883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34017b2411195fab012b203988be1cbbf77dc44e","tid":2058684,"uid":32947,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:57:09.000Z","msg":"好心你俾隻狗瞓覺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"未見到太陽升起果日 我地全家郁唔會訓架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9041709d0e7b49a2d0